pageType: content
background:
  type: solid
  color: "$background"
elements:
  - elementId: conv-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 45, 250, 22]
    content:
      style: "$label"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>PROCESS</p>

  - elementId: conv-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 75, 800, 40]
    content:
      style: "$heading"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>Converting Wireframes to Prototypes</p>

  - elementId: conv-accent-bar
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 125, 50, 3]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"

  - elementId: step1-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 155, 373, 130]
    shapeName: roundRect
    adjustments: [8000]
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$cardFill"

  - elementId: step1-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 163, 55, 36]
    content:
      fontSize: 28
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      color: "$accent"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>01</p>

  - elementId: step1-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [140, 163, 273, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      color: "$primary"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>IMPORT WIREFRAMES</p>

  - elementId: step1-desc
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 203, 333, 65]
    content:
      fontSize: 15
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      color: "$secondary"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>Import or create your wireframes in the prototyping tool</p>

  - elementId: step2-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [453, 155, 374, 130]
    shapeName: roundRect
    adjustments: [8000]
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$cardFill"

  - elementId: step2-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [473, 163, 55, 36]
    content:
      fontSize: 28
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      color: "$accent"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>02</p>

  - elementId: step2-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [533, 163, 274, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      color: "$primary"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>DEFINE HOTSPOTS</p>

  - elementId: step2-desc
    elementType: text
    bounds: [473, 203, 334, 65]
    content:
      fontSize: 15
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      color: "$secondary"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>Identify all clickable elements: buttons, links, cards</p>

  - elementId: step3-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [847, 155, 373, 130]
    shapeName: roundRect
    adjustments: [8000]
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$cardFill"

  - elementId: step3-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [867, 163, 55, 36]
    content:
      fontSize: 28
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      color: "$accent"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>03</p>

  - elementId: step3-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [927, 163, 273, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      color: "$primary"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>CREATE CONNECTIONS</p>

  - elementId: step3-desc
    elementType: text
    bounds: [867, 203, 333, 65]
    content:
      fontSize: 15
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      color: "$secondary"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>Link screens together via hotspot definitions</p>

  - elementId: step4-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 305, 373, 130]
    shapeName: roundRect
    adjustments: [8000]
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$cardFill"

  - elementId: step4-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 313, 55, 36]
    content:
      fontSize: 28
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      color: "$accent"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>04</p>

  - elementId: step4-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [140, 313, 273, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      color: "$primary"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>SET TRANSITIONS</p>

  - elementId: step4-desc
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 353, 333, 65]
    content:
      fontSize: 15
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      color: "$secondary"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>Choose instant, dissolve, slide, or smart animate</p>

  - elementId: step5-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [453, 305, 374, 130]
    shapeName: roundRect
    adjustments: [8000]
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$cardFill"

  - elementId: step5-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [473, 313, 55, 36]
    content:
      fontSize: 28
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      color: "$accent"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>05</p>

  - elementId: step5-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [533, 313, 274, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      color: "$primary"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>ADD SCROLLING</p>

  - elementId: step5-desc
    elementType: text
    bounds: [473, 353, 334, 65]
    content:
      fontSize: 15
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      color: "$secondary"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>Configure fixed headers and scrollable content areas</p>

  - elementId: step6-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [847, 305, 373, 130]
    shapeName: roundRect
    adjustments: [8000]
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$cardFill"

  - elementId: step6-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [867, 313, 55, 36]
    content:
      fontSize: 28
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      color: "$accent"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>06</p>

  - elementId: step6-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [927, 313, 273, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      color: "$primary"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>PREVIEW & TEST</p>

  - elementId: step6-desc
    elementType: text
    bounds: [867, 353, 333, 65]
    content:
      fontSize: 15
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      color: "$secondary"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>Click through the prototype as a user would</p>

  - elementId: best-practice-card
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 470, 1160, 170]
    shapeName: roundRect
    adjustments: [6000]
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: bp-icon
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [90, 490, 28, 28]
    iconName: "fas:star"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"

  - elementId: bp-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [130, 490, 300, 28]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      color: "$accent"
      letterSpacing: 2
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>BEST PRACTICE</p>

  - elementId: bp-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [90, 530, 1100, 90]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      color: "$light"
      lineHeight: 1.6
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>Start with the <strong style="color:$accent;">"happy path"</strong> — the ideal user flow that accomplishes the primary goal. Once the main journey works smoothly, then handle edge cases, error states, and alternate paths.</p>

  - elementId: conv-bottom-bar
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 690, 1160, 3]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"
